Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwith Trafalgar Law and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy entered a fighting competition \N- in which a winner will
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,get the Flare-Flare Fruit as the \Nprize - and won the first round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Rebecca, the gladiator \Ngirl Luffy supports,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nis fighting hard in the last match of the first round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Big Surprise!\NA True Identity of the Toy Soldier!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-L-L....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You must be Bartolomeo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou were pretty impressive in the Block B match!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am, Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You know my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NLet's wish each other good luck in the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a guy who set out to the sea\Nwanting to be like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way was it to the \Nplace to watch the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, people keep \Nfalling one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?\NA stack of toys and trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one will fall there.\NGet out of his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there is such a huge \Njunkyard underneath the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have the slight suspicion that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you, sir, are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--King Riku?!\N--No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's King Riku?! That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the former king of Dressrosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...resorted to unbelievable \Nviolence and got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm deep underground now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer need to disguise myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't call me "King" anymore,\NCaptain Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FORMER KING OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,He's King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:45.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RIKU DOLDO III\N(REBECCA'S GRANDFATHER)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NI'm so happy to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just another old man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sinful old man who can't \Neven save his own granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Doflamingo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're watching over Viola.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I disbelieve\Na dutiful man like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing compared with\Nwhat you've gone through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! You are King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're the king of Prodence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my kingdom when we \Nwere in trouble many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've been gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the countries around here lost balance\Nand there's been war after war!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick and tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Elizabello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're tired of it but \Neach time somebody cries,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsomebody else laughs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is agitating the countries to fight\Nand making millions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By selling tons of weapons\Nto those countries at war!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy... That broker is named Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Doflamingo's alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know where they manufacture \Nthose weapons or keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our country, the Kano Kingdom,\Nis at war now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're in trouble because the \Nenemy keeps getting weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We entered the competition in the Colosseum\Njust to search for the weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Happo Navy's true purpose is\Nto break down the smuggling ring of weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by the request of the king\Nof the Kano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:10:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku! Because you did such a foolish thing\Nand Doflamingo became king,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the neighboring countries are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Elizabello-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we were deeply indebted to\NDressrosa in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no need to keep affection for\Nthat man anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name "King Riku" is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Dagama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what really \Nhappened 10 years ago -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe tragedy of that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't talk shit\Nabout the king's personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tank! It's okay!\NIt's too late to say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}, I, too, was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a soldier of the army!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too, King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The toys are starting to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were all broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa's former soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even the toys are bowing to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought all the people hated King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Since they have this wide area here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...something more underground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?!\NWhat is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with this annoying crap!\NWhoever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you hurt Sai, I'll carry my anger \Neven towards your grandchildren!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sticky thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away! Hey, stop!\NWho are you?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done so you can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not harm any human\Nand follow any orders from the Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go straight out that door,\Nthere is a factory and a trade port.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No talking! Just work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since the contenders were all so powerful,\Nthey're not gonna break easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on?!\NI can't move my own body as I want!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only can move as he directed me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is happening to me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:18.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FLOWER FIELD\NTHE KING RIKU ARMY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, the ancestors of the Tontatta Tribe\Nkept going out to the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...looking for natural resources\Nthat their land lacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Big Humans kept discovering them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were facing extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found them! The Little People!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, the king of Dressrosa,\None of the neighboring countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,offered them a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he would provide \Nresources and guarantee
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their safety in exchange \Nfor a little bit of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That king's name was Don Quixote!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That led to the worst times of\Nthe Tontatta Tribe's history...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which continued on until 900 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The slave era!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some surviving manuscripts that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,describe how cruel the royal family was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were literally like devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ancestors were forced to work and work
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ndeep underground unnoticed by anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while the Big Humans were \Nliving lavishly on the wealth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nprovided by the work of the Tontatta Tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Records from the subsequent Hundred Year Void\Nare lost
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but 800 years ago,\Na new king took the throne of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When King Riku heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the Little People were being treated\Nas less than humans for centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he cried and apologized profusely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the new king devised\Na form of compensation for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told them they
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could simply take anything\Nthat they needed from the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, my bag is gone!\N--So is my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My jacket got stolen, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Shusui that was here a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stole from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fairies who took your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairies are fairies.\NAll you can do is laugh it off and let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I laugh it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those invisible fairies are\Nthe guardian deities of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa from ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to turn a blind \Neye to whatever they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, if fairies did it...\N--We should just forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king called it the work of fairies and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,calmed his citizens down by laughing it off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he established successfully the \Nlegend of fairies in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cool! The first King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The country was governed by\Nthe gentle Riku Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unstintingly supporting its neighboring countries\Nwhen they were in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say the country was wealthy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it became renowned\Nand the people were always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ancestors paid tribute\Nto King Riku's kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they voluntarily filled the country with\Nlots of greens and beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we Tontatta Kingdom and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the successive Riku Family \Ndeepened our bonds over 800 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, after 900 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo, the descendent of\Nthe Don Quixote Family, has returned
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he is trying\Nto repeat that horrible history!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter - Mancherie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and 500 of our people already \Nfell victim to that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let him repeat history!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The return of the Don Quixote line is\Ndoing Dressrosa and Tontatta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no good -- and much harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight with the heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland will help us tremendously!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's exactly what I was thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku is a good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has been so nice\Neven to these worm-like people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just call us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant it in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rot in hell, granddaughter of King Riku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Drop dead, Rebecca!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gladiator girl who is fighting\Nin the Colosseum is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being called King Riku's granddaughter\Nand getting insulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the people\Nof this country hate King Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was an incident in which \NKing Riku lost the trust
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nof all his citizens overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king was trying to protect \Nhis country until the end but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The corrupted King Riku's family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Screw you, Rebecca!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cut her to pieces!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people don't know\Nwhat really happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo tried to kill every \Nmember of the King Riku Family
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I took Rebecca who has\NKing Riku's blood in her veins
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ran away for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she got caught in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they keep her\Non public display at the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can regain the people's trust in King Riku\Nand save Rebecca's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind sacrificing my life\Nanytime, anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put everything on the line for this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect Rebecca's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget what happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't remember me\Nafter I turned into a toy but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san is a brave man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:23:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will always be by your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rebecca's real father!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
